Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.89,0:03:30.73,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Sex Pistols! \N Grab hold of the hook and stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.15,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,N-No good! \N It's pulling us in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.16,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,We're not strong enough for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.16,0:03:41.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Sh-Shit... I've gotta find {\i1}it...{\i0} {just to answer the question of what "it" is: the ice cube in Pesci's mouth. I threw emphasis on "it" so viewers know to expect the reveal of what "it" is (almost a minute later). -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:43.66,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I've gotta find it before it's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.08,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:48.42,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Gotta find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:50.13,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,We gotta find it no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.13,0:03:51.42,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Find it!
