Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:04.20,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I {\i1}knew{\i0} the asshole had to be cooling himself... \N This'll totally freak him out!{OLD: I knew the bastard had to be cooling himself off, \N so this should make him sweat a bit!}{Lit. "The bastard must be cooling himself, too... And this'll throw him off completely!" "sweat a bit" doesn't quite reach that. Old comment from TLC-san: "I dunno, the phrasing here is weird. The first half of the line is straight-forward enough, but the second half is like 'Enough so that he'll forget his reasoning'". -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.20,0:05:05.70,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,D-Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:08.29,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,How could you?! \N My ice...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.21,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's screamin' and looks white as a sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.29,0:05:11.21,Secondary,Pesci,0,0,0,,My ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.38,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Could this guy be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.13,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,It's him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.13,0:05:17.84,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He's the dude with the line and hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:21.30,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,That fishing-rod-looking thing is his Stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:22.68,Thoughts,Pesci,0,0,0,,{\an8}I-I gotta scram!
