Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.98,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.69,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Outta the way, ya old fossil!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:35.57,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Get your stinkin' zombie hands off of{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:39.99,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,My body feels so heavy, \N I don't want to move...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.99,0:05:43.53,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I ordered a real fatty cut of steak...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:45.91,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...but I don't feel like eating it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.33,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Get offa me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.41,0:05:52.79,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Yahoo! Got his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.79,0:05:54.38,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Get Mista over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.38,0:05:56.84,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,C'mon over here, Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:01.72,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.68,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,We got the enemy user!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:26.53,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Sex Pistols! \N All of you, back in the chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.13,0:06:42.26,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,It won't make a difference \N whether you answer me or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.26,0:06:48.72,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...but I'm going to ask you one \N very, {\i1}very{\i0} simple question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:54.44,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,If you don't answer within \N two seconds of me asking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:58.81,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...I'm putting a bullet in \N each of your eye sockets...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.32,0:07:01.61,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Uno, due...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:04.53,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,That's all the time you got, capisce?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.53,0:07:06.86,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,So here goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:10.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Where the hell is your friend hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.74,0:07:12.87,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Uno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:16.37,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,L-Like I know! \N I dunno where he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:18.71,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Due... Then die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:22.88,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Hey... Please help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.55,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I've always loved fatty cuts of steak...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.85,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,{\an8}...but I don't feel like eating it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:30.47,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Hey! Out of my way! \N You'll get your appetite back real soon, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.47,0:07:33.85,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,No, it just doesn't sound good anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:37.56,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Especially not for you, Mista. {Gah. Japanese with their omitting the subject of lines... With how the Japanese is phrased, it can entirely be seen as him talking about Mista throughout this entire rant. -TLC}{TLC again in the distant future here, honestly this kinda works though? Like the literal is like "Used to want steak but now don't want steak anymore!" "Don't worry, will want steak again soon!" "No, will never be able to eat anything again... BUT THAT IS YOU I AM TALKING ABOUT!!!" so yeah, just, Japanese being able to form grammatically coherent sentences without specifying subjects. But honestly the "doesn't sound good... FOR YOU!!!" thing kinda works as a solution? -Future TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.56,0:07:39.65,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Wh-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.61,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Grateful Dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:51.08,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:53.95,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Are you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.95,0:07:57.29,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You crafty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.59,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It works even faster through direct contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.59,0:08:06.13,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,My power is at its strongest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:10.55,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...while Grateful Dead touches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.10,0:08:13.26,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,P-Pistols...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.52,Thoughts,Mista,0,0,0,,I-It's too fast... No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:25.61,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-Is that you, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.78,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Are you really Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.78,0:08:30.95,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-I had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:33.70,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Y-You were here the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:39.46,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-I can't believe you aged yourself \N to blend in with the other passengers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:50.05,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Bro! Prosciutto! \N You're the coolest!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.39,0:08:58.14,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,{\an8}S-Stop that! \N Why are you so mad, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.76,0:08:59.39,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You fucking idiot! \N What the hell were you doing?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:02.98,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I didn't think he'd shoot the ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.98,0:09:04.86,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,What could I have done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:08.74,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You still don't get it? \N Pesci, you fucking mammone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.74,0:09:11.66,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Please quit hitting me, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:18.41,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Listen up! \N I'm only pissed off because you lack resolve, Pesci! {Nit: not a huge fan of "lack resolve" for 心の弱さ (lit. "heart's/mind's weakness"). Is this Prosciutto enough? -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:24.67,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I don't blame you for being shocked \N after those things got rid of all your ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.92,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I'm being aged too, so I know how it feels...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:32.26,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,But if it had been \N any other person on our team...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.26,0:09:38.14,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...they wouldn't have called their Stand back \N when they were that close to finishing off the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:41.39,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Even if it meant losing an arm or leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:44.44,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're a complete mammone, Pesci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.48,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You lost your cool. \N You're such a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.48,0:09:49.28,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It wasn't because of the ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.28,0:09:53.07,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,There's fear lurking deep within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.07,0:09:55.74,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It's time to grow up, Pesci.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.95,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,If you don't, we'll never make it big.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.95,0:10:01.50,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,We'll never defeat Buccellati and his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.04,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,And just so we're clear...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:09.67,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,We're not some bunch of losers that hang around \N pickup artist alleys or social clubs...{OLD: Our team isn't some stupid club \N filled with a bunch of losers...} {bluesun's idea for this and the next line: "random idea: We're not the sort of losers that go patting each others' heads and bragging 'we're gonna get em sometime' at flirting hotspots or buddies clubs" -QC A}{...what's the literal TL here? This seems pretty dang liberal -G}{The funny thing is... It actually isn't. This is actually pretty literal as-is. -TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:18.64,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...patting each other on the back \N and boasting how we're "gonna get 'em" someday.{OLD: ...who waste their breath boasting about \N killing people and cheering each other on.} {so, ぶっ殺す comes up here again, just like in 14. What we use in 14 should line up with what we have here, as well as the next line. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:22.77,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Once our mind's made up \N to {\i1}get{\i0} someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:26.56,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...the deed's already been done! {Should this line reference episode 14, line 55/56? "As of right now, those lines are "By the time phrases like that enter the minds of people like us, we've already killed the target, and our work's done with!" -G}{The Japanese wording does not match up so it's fine if the wording is different here too. Literal for this line is "At that moment the action has already been finished!" -TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:38.74,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Let's go, Pesci.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.87,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Here, have some ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:47.59,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You mentioned sensing another presence in \N the driver's compartment earlier, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.21,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I don't know how they're all hiding in there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:53.47,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...but the girl's in the driver's compartment!
Comment: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:57.01,Main,,0,0,0,,C
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.48,0:11:12.28,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Don't worry about Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:17.70,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Save that ice for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.57,0:11:20.83,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,You need to keep \N your {\i1}own{\i0} body chilled. {missed a だけ, so I added *own*. - The Bucc is emphasizing that she needs to focus on keeping herself alive. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.83,0:11:26.92,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,Fanning him with air or cooling him \N with a wet towel won't have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.92,0:11:29.75,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,The only thing that can help him is ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.25,0:11:33.63,Main,Trish,0,0,0,,He'll be the first to die at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:38.72,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Narancia and the rest of us are prepared to \N follow the boss's orders, no matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.72,0:11:42.39,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Your biggest concern \N should be your own safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.39,0:11:44.81,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Your safety is our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:48.23,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,It's not as if you chose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.65,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,As for the enemy who's causing us all to age...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.19,0:11:54.40,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Mista will take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:57.74,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'm sure... he'll figure something out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.49,0:11:59.57,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Mista...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:18.68,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I think I finally have a good idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.68,0:12:20.22,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...where, and how, they're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.06,0:12:27.31,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I need to think outside of the box \N in order to find them. {literally says 4D, man's ahead of his time}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:32.77,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Buccellati received some kind of \N dark object from the boss at the station. {changed "black" to "dark." 黒い can also mean "dark", and that seems more appropriate given the color of the object wasn't clear from Prosciutto's POV. -QC A}{This should be consistent with how the object is described in episode 14, line 104 -G}{WELL IT'S A GOOD THING I REWROTE THAT LINE TO SAY "DARK OBJECT" BEFORE EVEN SEEING THIS NOTE THEN :D -TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:36.32,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,That's it. That's what I need to look for\N in the driver's compartment!{This is not a line that should be split at the period. It becomes a thousand times too lopsided that way. -TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:39.57,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Hey, Pesci...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:45.08,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,What do you think the \N other presence you felt in here was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.54,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Do you still feel it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:51.58,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,A-About that... Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.58,0:12:54.55,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I wouldn't put too much faith in me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:56.30,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I ain't so smart... {I'm not -> I ain't, to emphasize his point and better match his JP -QC A}{I approve of this Okuyasuism -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.30,0:12:59.68,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Pesci, Pesci, Pesci, Pesci...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.68,0:13:02.64,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.85,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,If you're still upset \N that I yelled at you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.85,0:13:08.02,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...you just need to be confident. {OLD: gain more confidence}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:14.48,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,If you really put your mind to it, \N your Beach Boy's ability would be unbeatable!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.65,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:21.32,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,That presence you felt earlier \N is {\i1}extremely{\i0} suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:24.12,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It's do or die time, Pesci.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.91,0:13:29.16,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with \N being confident in your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:30.62,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.71,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Yes, really!{Of course!} {more like he's repeating そう right back at him -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:35.71,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Try to remember. \N It doesn't matter how unimportant it seemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:38.42,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Did you see anything strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:41.38,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Maybe some dark-looking thing?{OLD: Maybe something that looked black?}{Changed this and the next line based on my previous observation -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.35,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Huh? \N Some... dark-looking thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:47.10,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,That's it, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.48,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I was gonna look under \N the driver's seat earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.48,0:13:52.77,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I noticed something super weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:01.99,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... \N Guess I was just imagining it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:08.99,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I knew it... \N You shouldn't have counted on my instincts{Note, the word he uses here is "kan", the exact same word that Buccellati praises Prosciutto for later. Probably worth paying attention to. -TLC}, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:08.99,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, it looks like you were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.70,0:14:10.95,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Come again? {Too professional sounding for Pesci -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:12.79,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Excellent work, Pesci.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.79,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,This mystery is solved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:17.59,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I finally get it thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.38,0:14:20.46,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,B-Bro? \N Wh-What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:25.84,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Why is there animal shit \N near the driver's seat all of a sudden? {added "all of a sudden". missed いきなり -QC A}
Comment: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:23.13,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,{\an8}I don't get it! {I commented this out because it's hard to hear and not important compared to Prosciutto's line. In case it needs to be uncommented, I made it \an8 instead of secondary font since Prosciutto's is now a double line -G}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.76,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It's not mouse shit, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:32.98,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,If it were just some rodent, \N it would've dropped dead by now. {OLD: If it were a mouse, it'd be dead by now.}{"...lying here..."? The point does seem to be that there's poop but no corpse in sight. -TLC} {mmh... probably the implication, but I think this line exists more to tie in with the next line -- the poop's fresh, according to his earlier reaction, and he points this out moments later. Other issues: missed とか after ネズミ, so probably better to say "some rodent". くたばってる is a much less polite of saying "die", as Jisho seems to indicate: "drop dead", "kick the bucket", etc. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:37.06,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The shit's not old, either. \N Looks like it was just freshly deposited.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:40.28,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,So what does that tell you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:44.49,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Humans aren't the only beings \N who can possess Stand abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.82,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,This can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:49.37,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...the animal is moving through the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.50,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Grateful Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:57.67,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wh-What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:15:00.50,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,I-It's a tortoise? A tortoise?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:02.92,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Found her! It's Trish!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.72,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I can see the others, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:09.01,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Just like I thought, \N everyone except Trish is dying of old age!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:10.56,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,That settles it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.56,0:15:13.68,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I'll concentrate my aging ability \N right into the tortoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:15.85,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Grateful Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.40,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Wait a sec, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.61,0:15:22.61,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Isn't... one of them missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:26.74,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,One of them isn't there anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.64,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista! Please get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.64,0:15:54.73,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,This is all the ice I got left, \N but please feel better!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.35,0:16:00.98,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,I dunno if it's thanks to my attentive nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.98,0:16:04.74,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...or if I just barely lucked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:12.37,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,But since I put one of the ice cubes \N I picked up earlier inside my hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.37,0:16:20.33,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Number Five... It looks like you were \N the only one who had the effects of the aging reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:27.42,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,You did good stopping those bullets for me... \N All three of 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.72,0:16:33.60,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,Number Five... \N I have one more request...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.60,0:16:39.85,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,If you wanted me to go to Buccellati, \N I already revived Number Six and sent him over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.85,0:16:47.07,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,He took the ice in your pocket and went to tell them \N two enemies were headed for the tortoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.07,0:16:55.62,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,That's good... I don't need the ice anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.95,0:16:58.41,Main,Mista,0,0,0,,...after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.41,0:17:00.25,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Mista!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:04.88,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,It's Buccellati, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:08.09,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Buccellati's the missing one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:10.43,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if Buccellati's in there or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.43,0:17:13.05,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,All that matters is that we take Trish alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:14.64,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Grateful Dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.10,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:22.56,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Sharp instincts. \N And you're fast, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.56,0:17:25.02,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I just have to defeat {\i1}him,{\i0} right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.19,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The one in black! {Here, black is fine since he's clearly wearing black threads. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:29.07,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You got it, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.07,0:17:33.20,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Everyone's aging'll be reversed if you beat him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.20,0:17:36.41,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,What the fuck is Mista's Stand doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.41,0:17:42.17,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I pulled the trigger myself and put three bullets \N through his head, point-blank... didn't I?{OLD: I personally shot three pointblank bullets \N through his head... didn't I?}{point-blank is hyphenated. Also, point-blank isn't typically used to directly modify a noun, despite being an adjective... kind of an odd duck as a stand-alone concept. Rewrote the line to better reflect typical usage. -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:45.00,Thoughts,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,So what is that thing \N doing here with an ice cube?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:47.00,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Don't let it touch ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:50.38,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,You'll age super-duper fast if it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:54.68,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.31,0:18:07.52,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,H-He's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.07,0:18:12.61,Main,Pesci,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.61,0:18:14.20,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.20,0:18:16.41,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Deal with everyone in the tortoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:20.41,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Make it fast!{OLD: Hurry up!} \N Kill the rest of his crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:33.93,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Wasn't that a bit careless of you, Buccellati?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:38.56,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,After Mista went through \N all that trouble to warn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.56,0:18:42.77,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Defeating me, even if it costs \N the lives of your crew, to protect the girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.44,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Isn't that your mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:49.11,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're a failure of a capo! \N Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.44,0:18:53.28,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.29,0:19:04.75,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I will complete this mission...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:06.50,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,...and I'll protect my crew, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.50,0:19:12.09,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,That shouldn't be difficult \N if I'm only facing the likes of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.88,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It's fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.72,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It's really fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:24.77,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Your... Sticky Fingers, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.77,0:19:29.15,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,It definitely seems faster than my Stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.15,0:19:35.20,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,But you don't seem to fully understand \N the implications of going fast, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:42.54,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I may be out of breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.92,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...but so are you, Buccellati.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:57.22,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Since we both used our Stands at full speed, \N we burned a lot of energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.22,0:20:02.39,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You didn't get that and attacked me \N as fast as you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:06.60,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...and now you're aging again \N even though you're standing in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:13.40,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The more horsepower a car has, \N the warmer it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.40,0:20:16.03,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're burning calories like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.03,0:20:20.45,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You're a smart guy, \N so I'm sure you can figure out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.45,0:20:23.74,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,...what will happen if your body \N keeps getting warmer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:29.46,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,B-Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.25,0:20:34.17,Main,Sex Pistols,0,0,0,,Th-The ice isn't working anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.17,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,So what are you going to do now, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.17,0:20:41.93,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The zipper you put on me is starting to close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:44.97,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,The one on my chin is already gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.39,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.23,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Exhausted from your stiff shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.52,0:20:53.32,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Sticky Fingers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:57.03,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,I see what you're doing! \N You're too slow, Buccellati!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:02.74,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Got you! You're all done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:05.58,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,We'll be taking the boss's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.58,0:21:09.62,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I was prepared for what would happen \N if my body warmed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.46,0:21:13.38,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I was also prepared to get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:15.50,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} complete this mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.50,0:21:17.42,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,I'll protect my crew, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:22.43,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,The hardest part about being a capo \N is that I've sworn to do both.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.43,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Are {\i1}you{\i0} prepared? {emphasis on "you" here -- he's pretty pointed in this context -QC A}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.89,0:21:27.35,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Because I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:28.14,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Wha{\fscx300}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.06,0:21:30.56,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,Y-You can't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.56,0:21:32.69,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You son of a bitch! \N You're kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.77,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Doing both is a simple matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:39.03,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,If I can get you off this train...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:44.24,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,As long as I can reverse the aging, my five subordinates will be back, and they'll be able to protect Trish! {Should there be an "Even" at the start of this line? "Even if this is all I can do, my subordinates will finish the job" -G}{No idea where "all I can do" even came from. He says that as long as he manages to undo the aging, then they've won because his crew can handle the rest. It's less of an "all I can do" kind of idea and more of an "all I NEED TO do" one. So, changed to "As long as I can"-TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.24,0:21:47.79,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You asshole! \N Y-You're fucking insane! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.00,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,We're moving at 150 kilometers an hour!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.00,0:21:53.46,Main,Bruno,0,0,0,,Oh, come on. \N You're the one who grabbed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:04.97,Main,Prosciutto,0,0,0,,You got a fucking death wish, motherfucker?!
